room.title: 你是我的城池营垒 白敬亭
room.challenge_info: {"cid":"1568352984860673","cha_name":"白敬亭","desc":"白敬亭，1993年10月15日出生于北京市怀柔区，中国内地男演员，毕业于首都师范大学音乐学院。 2014年，因参演搜狐自制网剧《匆匆那年》，饰演男二号“乔燃”一角受到关注 。2015年7月，参演明晓溪同名小说改编电视剧《旋风少女》，在剧中饰演喻初原 ；2015年10月，参与的自然旅游纪实真人秀《跟着贝尔去冒险》播出 。2016年，参与的明星推理综艺秀《明星大侦探》播出；4月22日，主演的青春电影《谁的青春不迷茫》上映；7月15日，加盟江苏卫视真人秀《我们战斗吧》 。2017年年初，参与《明星大侦探第二季》录制 ；同年1月，参与的真人秀《触不到的TA》播出 ；4月22日，出任第七届中国大学生电视节青春代言人 ；6月11日主演电视剧《夏至未至》在湖南卫视开播，饰演陆之昂；9月起，参与《明星大侦探第三季》录制 。2018年2月2日，参加的《二十四小时第三季》在浙江卫视播出。\r\n2019年11月，白敬亭参演《青春环游记》第二季阵容，节目将在2020年第二季度周六晚黄金档播出。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1568352984860673","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token":false,"fb_expire_time":0,"tw_expire_time":0,"has_youtube_token":false,"youtube_expire_time":0,"room_id":0,"live_verify":0,"authority_status":0,"verify_info":"","shield_follow_notice":0,"shield_digg_notice":0
